text: Macrozamia plurinervia is a species of plant in the family Zamiaceae. It is endemic to Australia. Its natural habitat is subtropical or tropical dry forests. ==References== plurinervia Category:Flora of New South Wales Category:Flora of Queensland Category:Cycadophyta of Australia Category:Endemic flora of Australia Category:Least concern flora of Australia Category:Near threatened biota of Queensland Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
